metadata.name: Ethereal 001 / ALPS
metadata.description:
Ethereal is a lifelong and future-oriented NFT art project born at the intersection of the physical and the digital to immortalize the ethereal existence of our planet.

Title: Alps
Edition: 1/1
Artist: Alexander Zaxarov
Year: 2016
Medium: Digital Photography
